java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag
public class WebEventDispatchTag
extends javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport

Title: JSP Tag which calls the web event dispatcher

Description: Custom JSP Tag which calls the WebEventDispatch dispatcher, and determines whether or not to process the rest of the page.

doEndTag

public int doEndTag()
             throws javax.servlet.jsp.JspTagException
Handles the eng tag. Calls the WebEventDispatch.dispatch() function, passing in the request and response from the current pageContext and the loginRequired boolean from the value of the loginRequired attribute.
Overrides:
doEndTag in class javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport
Returns:
Returns EVAL_PAGE if the web event dispatcher returns true, otherwise returns SKIP_PAGE.
Throws:
javax.servlet.jsp.JspTagException - Standard J2EE JspTagException
